# Users API Test
# Make sure the backend server is running on http://localhost:5000

### Get all users (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get user by ID (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Update user (requires authentication)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Updated Name",
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "bio": "Updated bio",
  "address": "Updated address",
  "role": "user"
}

### Delete user (requires authentication)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Toggle user status (requires authentication)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/users/USER_ID_HERE/toggle-status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE